"            ເລກອ້າງອີງ: <t t-out=\"object.partner_ref or ''\">REF_XXX</t>\n"
"        </t>\n"
"        ຈາກ <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or ''\">YourCompany</t>.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        ຫາກທ່ານມີຄຳຖາມໃດໆ, ກະລຸນາຕິດຕໍ່ຫາພວກເຮົາໄດ້ທຸກເວລາ.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        ດ້ວຍຄວາມນັບຖື,\n"
"        <t t-if=\"not is_html_empty(object.user_id.signature)\">\n"
"            <br><br>\n"
"            <t t-out=\"object.user_id.signature or ''\">--<br>Mitchell "
"Admin</t>\n"
"        </t>\n"
"    </p>\n"
"</div>"

