#. module: purchase
#: model_terms:digest.tip,tip_description:purchase.digest_tip_purchase_0
msgid "When creating a purchase order, have a look at the vendor's <i>On Time Delivery</i> rate: the percentage of products shipped on time. If it is too low, activate the <i>automated reminders</i>. A few days before the due shipment, Odoo will send the vendor an email to ask confirmation of shipment dates and keep you informed in case of any delays. To get the vendor's performance statistics, click on the OTD rate."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງອັດຕາ <i>ການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງກົງເວລາ</i> ຂອງຜູ້ສະໜອງ: ເປີເຊັນຂອງສິນຄ້າທີ່ສົ່ງກົງເວລ"
"າ. ຫາກມັນຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ, ໃຫ້ເປີດໃຊ້ <i>ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນອັດຕະໂນມັດ</i>. ສອງສາມມື້ກ່ອນກຳນົດສົ່ງ, Odoo ຈະ"
"ສົ່ງອີເມວຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງເພື່ອຂໍການຢືນຢັນວັນທີສົ່ງ ແລະ ແຈ້ງໃຫ້ທ່ານຊາບຫາກມີການລ່າຊ້າ. ເພື່ອເບິ່ງສະຖິຕິປະສິດທິພາບ"
"ຂອງຜູ້ສະໜອງ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ອັດຕາ OTD."

#. module: purchase
#: model_terms:digest.tip,tip_description:purchase.digest_tip_purchase_1
msgid "When sending a purchase order by email, Odoo asks the vendor to acknowledge the reception of the order. When the vendor acknowledges the order by clicking on a button in the email, the information is added on the purchase order. Use filters to track orders that have not been acknowledged."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສົ່ງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທາງອີເມວ, Odoo ຈະຂໍໃຫ້ຜູ້ສະໜອງຕອບຮັບການຮັບໃບສັ່ງຊື້. ເມື່ອຜູ້ສະໜອງຕອບຮັບໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ"
"ໃນອີເມວ, ຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນໃບສັ່ງຊື້. ໃຊ້ຕົວຕອງເພື່ອຕິດຕາມໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ຮັບການຕອບຮັບ."

#. module: purchase
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:purchase.field_purchase_order__partner_id
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:purchase.field_purchase_order_line__partner_id
msgid "You can find a vendor by its Name, TIN, Email or Internal Reference."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຄົ້ນຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງໄດ້ໂດຍ ຊື່, ເລກປະຈຳຕົວຜູ້ເສຍພາສີ, ອີເມວ ຫຼື ເລກອ້າງອີງພາຍໃນ."

#. module: purchase
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/purchase/models/purchase.py:0
#, python-format
msgid "You cannot change the type of a purchase order line. Instead you should delete the current line and create a new line of the proper type."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນປະເພດຂອງລາຍການໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້. ທ່ານຄວນລຶບລາຍການປະຈຸບັນ ແລະ ສ້າງລາຍການໃໝ່ດ້ວຍປະເພ"
"ດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງແທນ."

#. module: purchase
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:purchase.product_product_action
msgid ""
"You must define a product for everything you sell or purchase,\n"
"                whether it's a storable product, a consumable or a service."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດຜະລິດຕະພັນສຳລັບທຸກສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຂາຍ ຫຼື ຊື້,\n"
"                ບໍ່ວ່າຈະເປັນຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ເກັບສາງໄດ້, ເຄື່ອງບໍລິໂພກ ຫຼື ການບໍລິການ."

#. module: purchase
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:purchase.product_normal_action_puchased
msgid ""
"You must define a product for everything you sell or purchase,\n"
"            whether it's a storable product, a consumable or a service."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດສິນຄ້າສຳລັບທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ທ່ານຂາຍ ຫຼື ຊື້, \n"
"            ບໍ່ວ່າຈະເປັນສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈັດເກັບໄດ້, ສິນຄ້າທີ່ໃຊ້ໝົດໄປ ຫຼື ການບໍລິການ."

#. module: purchase
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/purchase/models/purchase.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your quotation contains products from company %(product_company)s whereas your quotation belongs to company %(quote_company)s. \n"
" Please change the company of your quotation or remove the products from other companies (%(bad_products)s)."
msgstr ""
"ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານມີສິນຄ້າຈາກບໍລິສັດ %(product_company)s ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານເປັນຂອ"
"ງບໍລິສັດ %(quote_company)s. \n"
" ກະລຸນາປ່ຽນບໍລິສັດຂອງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ ຫຼື ລຶບສິນຄ້າຈາກບໍລິສັດອື່ນອອກ (%(bad_products)s)."

